Orla Couture:\ Orla has been within the city of Rinascita since she was a teenager. She arrived with little florins to her name and no family of her own. In her youth, she settled into a crowd of unsavory individuals which she used to make a living for herself. As an orphan in an unfamiliar city, few mentors were able to assist her. Prelate Antos of the Catholic Church took pity on her and assisted her in turning her life around. She then met Chesh and Tara who permitted her to join their guilds. First as a placeholder in the CV Mercenary Guild and then a clothier to the SoWeCanSew Guild. From there, Orla learned she had a passion and eye for fashion. She soon grew to love the career she was granted access to. Presently, she is recognized for creating hundreds of outfits and completing orders from those as high as Royalty to as low as the less fortunate. She has also been appointed the first new leader of the guild since it was created, passed down from Viscountess Tara herself. She hopes to continue keeping the guild blooming for years to come.\\r\\n\
